{{Infobox journal | title = Sicherheit und Frieden | cover = | discipline = [[Political science]], [[peace and conflict studies]] | language = German, English | publisher = Nomos | country = Germany | frequency = Quarterly | history = 1983–present | abbreviation=Sicherh. Frieden | openaccess = | website = http://www.security-and-peace.de/ | ISSN = 0175-274X }} '''''Sicherheit und Frieden''''' (English: ''Security and Peace'') is a quarterly German [[academic journal]] focusing on [[peace and conflict studies|peace research]] and [[security policy]] publishing articles in German and English. Since 2004 the journal also publishes [[peer review|peer-reviewed]] articles. The current [[editor-in-chief]] is [[Michael Brzoska]] (Institute for Peace Research and Security Policy, [[University of Hamburg]]).
